    "The specific query searched was: ((diabetes OR glucose) AND (AHP OR TOPSIS OR MCDM OR multi-criteria-decision-making)).",
    "Inclusion and Exclusion CriteriaWe initially eliminated any duplicate articles from various sources after receiving the results of an initial collection of relevant articles and then manually inspected the remaining articles to assess them under the inclusion criteria.",
    "The inclusion criteria were any English papers published between 2003 and 2023.",
    "Research, review, conference, and case report articles with an abstract or full text were taken into account.",
    "Non-English articles and other research forms, such as letters to editors and brief messages, were excluded."
